ntroduction:
The objective of this scenario is to establish a robust and secure AWS environment utilizing various AWS services including EC2 instances, a Load Balancer, Web Application Firewall (WAF),

Components:

EC2 Instances:
Launch EC2 instances to host your application or service.
Ensure that the EC2 instances are configured with the necessary security groups to restrict access appropriately.

Load Balancer:
Utilize an Application Load Balancer (ALB) or Network Load Balancer (NLB) based on your requirements.

Web Application Firewall (WAF):
Set up a Web Application Firewall (WAF) to protect your web applications from common web exploits.
Define rules in WAF to filter and monitor HTTP/HTTPS requests that are forwarded to the EC2 instances via the Load Balancer. test add Rate-based rule and originates from country

